            <td class="blob-code">    }</td>
            </tr>
    <tr>
                    <td class="line-number line-number-expandable" data-range="192-199" data-last="0">
                <i class="fa fa-arrows-v js-icon-load-more" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show Lines" data-placement="left"></i>
                <i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin js-icon-loading"></i>
            </td>
            <td class="gap-line">
                                                    ... lines 192 - 199
                            </td>
            </tr>
    <tr>
                    <td class="line-number line-number-displayed" data-line-number-displayed="200"></td>
            <td class="blob-code">}</td>
            </tr>

        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
</p>
<h2 id="have-fun-and-avoid-infinite-recursion">Have Fun and Avoid Infinite Recursion! <a class="headerlink" href="synchronizing-mapping-inverse#have-fun-and-avoid-infinite-recursion" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>That's great! Oh, except for one thing I just introduced: <strong>infinite recursion</strong>!
When we call <code>removeStudiedGenus()</code>, that calls <code>removeGenusScientist()</code>, which
calls <code>removeStudiedGenus()</code>, and so on... forever. And we are too busy to let our
scripts run forever!</p>
<p>The fix is easy - I was being lazy. Add an <code>if</code> statement in the remove functions,
like if <code>!$this-&gt;studiedGenuses-&gt;contains($genus)</code>, then just return:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="506832daff">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
                        <span class="js-expand-all" data-range="1-244" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show All Lines" data-placement="top">
                <i class="fa fa-expand js-icon-load-more"></i>
                <i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin js-icon-loading"></i>
            </span>
            
            244 lines <span class="meta-divider"></span> <span title="src/AppBundle/Entity/User.php">src/AppBundle/Entity/User.php</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <table class="hljs code-block-table">
        <tbody class="js-tr-container">
                <tr>
                    <td class="line-number line-number-expandable" data-range="1-16" data-last="0">
