</p>
<p>In other words, if the <code>$genus</code> is not in the <code>studiedGenuses</code> array, there's no reason
to try to remove it.</p>
<p>Inside <code>Genus</code>, do the exact same thing: if <code>!$this-&gt;genusScientists-&gt;contains($user)</code>,
then return:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="018f103b19">
